{"tid":940442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[先達翻生] 高通將阻蘋果在華銷售新iPhone","createTime":"2018-12-14T02:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T02:49:27.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4618adda49d0a22d24e60f7614f4123898081e4","tid":940442,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"晶片生產商高通證實，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>正尋求中國法院阻止蘋果銷售最新的iPhone型號XS與XR</strong></span>，主要是因應法院早前批准禁售較舊型號iPhone的銷售。<br />\n<br />\n周一，中國法院下令禁售較舊型號iPhone，基於高通稱有關產品侵犯了其專利。<br />\n<br />\n高通的代表律師Jiang Hongyi較早時接受《金融時報》訪問時披露上述消息。<br />\n<br />\n不過，蘋果稱所有型號iPhone仍可如常銷售，而該公司已經向中國法院呈現，要求重新考慮有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果未有回應查詢。"},{"pid":"2ad4357c9bb5af379a474e16c33c94934daebbd3","tid":940442,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:49:27.000Z","msg":"又冇得炒埃瘋啦，你班大陸仔仲唔畀我地當豬頭咁撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}